com.redhat.rhn.frontend.struts

Class XmlMessageResources

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.struts.util.MessageResources
      • com.redhat.rhn.frontend.struts.XmlMessageResources
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class XmlMessageResources
extends org.apache.struts.util.MessageResources
    XmlMessageResources - Class that extends Strut's mechanisms for providing localized text for the HTML frontend. This class fetches messages from RHN's LocalizationService: Any calls within RHN's web UI frontend will need to have corresponding keys in the XML resources file used by LocalizationService.
